    "text": [
        "Dear Anna,",
        "How have you been? I hope this letter finds you in good health and wealth. I am writing this to inform you that the importance of short breaks in between long working hours. I have read an article in a famous magazine called \"Vanita health\". Actually I was fascinating.",
        "The article is written by Dr.James he is one of the famous neurologists in Ramagiri hospital , in that he said that nowadays most of the people have a sedementary life especially after covid pandemic we have a remote work models. Sitting in front of a computer for a long time can cause detrimental effects on our brain eventually deprivation of neutrons may occur, hence it would develop a condition called dementia.",
        "When I read the article I have became scared because both we are spending a lot of time infront of electronic gadgets for our work. Instead of lengthy work he has been advice take a short work then relax for 5 minutes. For relaxing he suggests several activities like listening to music ,brisk walking ,meditation so on . I think the article is very useful and I Will share a copy along with the letter. Kindly go through.",
        "I am look forward to meeting from you.",
        "With love ,",
        "Krishna."
